Very sharp contact with the overlying dark material. It appears that the transition or contact with underlying dark unit was removed by IW sampling. Smear slide reveals very abundant nannofossils, abundant clay, common foraminifers and common biosilica (diatoms + radiolarians), so formal lithologic name is clayey nannofossil ooze with foraminifers and biosilica.
